<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { background: #000; color: #fff; text-align: center; font-family: Tahoma; padding-top: 20%; }
        .btn { 
            background: #22dd22; color: #000; padding: 20px; 
            text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 24px; display: inline-block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>WARGODS REPORT FOUND</h1>
    <p>The CS 1.6 browser cannot open secure links automatically.</p>
    <br>
    <a id="wgLink" class="btn" href="#">CLICK HERE TO VIEW REPORT</a>

    <script>
        var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
        var reportID = urlParams.get('id');
        if (reportID) {
            document.getElementById('wgLink').href = "https://www.wargods.ro/wcd/report.php?id=" + reportID;
        } else {
            document.body.innerHTML = "<h1>Error: No ID provided</h1>";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
